{"word":"σκεπτέος","slug":"σκεπτέος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>σκεπτέος</b></el> <el>(σκεπτέος, ον,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:verbal Adjective'>verb. <a href='S:Adjective'>adj.</a></a> of <a href='S:σκέπτομαι'><el>σκέπτομαι</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>one must reflect</i> or <i>consider</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><el>σκεπτέος, η, ον</el>, <i>to be considered, examined</i>, <b>Antipho.</b><p/></div>"}]}